Package org.locationtech.jts.triangulate.polygon

Classes for triangulating polygons.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstrainedDelaunayTriangulator
    Computes the Constrained Delaunay Triangulation of polygons.
    PolygonHoleJoiner
    Transforms a polygon with holes into a single self-touching (invalid) ring by joining holes to the exterior shell or to another hole.
    PolygonTriangulator
    Computes a triangulation of each polygon in a Geometry.

Package org.locationtech.jts.triangulate.polygon Description

Classes for triangulating polygons. ConstrainedDelaunayTriangulator can be used to provide high-quality near-Delaunay triangulations of polygonal geometry. The PolygonTriangulator produces lower-quality but faster triangulations.
